    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707170/extras/2240708c633896b8e7f05c7023c9d569.poster.avif?t=1745602511\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707170/extras/2240708c633896b8e7f05c7023c9d569.webm?t=1745602511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707170/extras/2240708c633896b8e7f05c7023c9d569.mp4?t=1745602511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《相扑塌米》的世界，在这里，笨拙的相扑选手在有趣而竞争的模式中进行比赛！准备与朋友和对手一起参加比赛、决斗、保龄球、高尔夫和其他相扑冒险。[ /p]<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤣 <strong>不可预测的相扑动作:</strong> 控制一个笨拙的摔跤手，在危险的竞技场中体验混乱。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707170/extras/a6df2648308fe6ac7c66af0cbe76dcf5.poster.avif?t=1745602511\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707170/extras/a6df2648308fe6ac7c66af0cbe76dcf5.webm?t=1745602511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707170/extras/a6df2648308fe6ac7c66af0cbe76dcf5.mp4?t=1745602511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 <strong>搞笑武器:</strong> 使用从火箭发射器到鱼叉的搞笑武器库。[ /p]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥇 <strong>比赛:</strong> 在充满笑声和兴奋的多种模式中争夺相扑冠军的头衔。[ /p]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707170/extras/b76ca5dad75ac5e808cb4e9569bc536a.poster.avif?t=1745602511\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707170/extras/b76ca5dad75ac5e808cb4e9569bc536a.webm?t=1745602511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707170/extras/b76ca5dad75ac5e808cb4e9569bc536a.mp4?t=1745602511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚀 <strong>奇怪的奖励:</strong> 获取强大的奖励以在战斗中主宰。[ /p]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎭 <strong>无数的皮肤:</strong> 为你的相扑选手穿上独特的服装和面具，让他在其他人中脱颖而出。[ /p]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707170/extras/460c7c0ba89b799a262caf3aeed4c2d5.poster.avif?t=1745602511\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707170/extras/460c7c0ba89b799a262caf3aeed4c2d5.webm?t=1745602511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707170/extras/460c7c0ba89b799a262caf3aeed4c2d5.mp4?t=1745602511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备在《相扑塌米》中享受乐趣和疯狂的战斗，这是聚会的完美平台！</p></p></p></p></p></p>",
